    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## AI Makes a Future Prediction\r\n\r\nPrompt AI Chat to develop a future prediction.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n<details open>\r\n<summary><strong>Step 1</strong></summary>\r\nCreate a prompt that will get AI Chat to make a prediction about the future of your topic. Remember to include:\r\n\r\n- Task\r\n- Context\r\n- Format\r\n- Reference (any artifacts you collected)\r\n- Tone\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n::: details [**Step 2**]\r\nConsider the following questions:\r\n- Does AI's prediction feel believable? Why or why not?\r\n- What supporting evidence or perspectives could strengthen this prediction?\r\n- What ethical concerns, if any, does this prediction raise?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Step 3**]\r\nRefine your initial prompt to increase accuracy and reduce bias. Make sure to:\r\n- Use the tips below to help you. \r\n- Remember to add all of your saved artifacts again.\r\n- Send your prompt to AI Chat and read its response.\r\n\r\n---\r\n**Tips for Better Results**\r\n- Ask the AI to predict based on current trends, research, or diverse perspectives.\r\n- Don't just accept the first answer - challenge it or ask for alternatives.\r\n- Want to make it more inclusive? Ask: _\"How might this affect different communities?\"_\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Step 4**]\r\nRepeat this process several times until you are satisfied with AI's prediction.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n",
